	(text "TODO:\n\nUSBC Port to the two USB pins. Also, you need to add two resistors to the USB-C port to specify that it's 5V so it works with C to C cables\nFlush out PWM Dimming Control (This is tail lights only, headlight dimming is done with pwm dimming pin & ESP32\nAdd all pins to LDH-65-700 Symbol (even unused ones)\n12V Stepdown is not placed, needs to be removed from the schematic. It's an external device. Replace with 12v nets and a generic 2 pin connector (tbd)\nFind a nice small surface mount normally open push button that we can use and insert their part numbers and link into the symbols"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 90.17 177.546 0)
		(effects
